Package org.alienideology.jcord.internal.gateway Description

Internal Gateway Connections

GatewayAdaptor is the listener to the Gateway connection with Discord. OPCode, DisconnectionCode, HttpCode, and ErrorResponse are enumerations representing codes and responses of Discord Gateway. HttpPath is where all the Http Requests' path go. It is set up for requesting Get, Post, Patch, Delete, etc methods.
